Regina Müller, Thomas Stamminger, and Manfred Marschall</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_567\">Cytomegaloviral protein kinase pUL97 interacts with the nuclear mRNA export factor pUL69 to modulate its intranuclear localization and activity</label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 567-578. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/567\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/567\">[Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/567\">[PDF]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/567/DC1\">[Supplementary Table]</a> &nbsp;</nobr>\n        <p></p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n    <dl>\n      <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/579\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_579\"> Jens Milbradt, Sabrina Auerochs, Heinrich Sticht, and Manfred Marschall</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_579\">Cytomegaloviral proteins that associate with the nuclear lamina: components of a postulated nuclear egress complex</label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 579-590. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/579\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/579\">[Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/579\">[PDF]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/579/DC1\">[Supplementary Material]</a> &nbsp;</nobr>\n        <p></p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n    <table width=\"100%\">\n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td bgcolor=\"#CCE0F9\">\n          <dl>\n            <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/591\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_591\"> Jessica Sorem and Richard Longnecker</dt>\n            <dd>\n              <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_591\">Cleavage of Epstein–Barr virus glycoprotein B is required for full function in cell–cell fusion with both epithelial and B cells</label></strong><br>\n              J Gen Virol 2009 90: 591-595. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/591\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/591\">[Free Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/591\">[PDF]</a> <strong><font color=\"#000090\">IMMEDIATE OPEN ACCESS ARTICLE</font></strong> &nbsp;</nobr>\n              <p></p>\n            </dd>\n          </dl>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody></table>\n    <dl>\n      <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/596\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_596\"> Kevin J. Colgan, James R. Boyne, and Adrian Whitehouse</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_596\">Identification of a response element in a herpesvirus saimiri mRNA recognized by the ORF57 protein</label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 596-601. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/596\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/596\">[Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/596\">[PDF]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/596/DC2\">[Supplementary Figure]</a><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/596/DC3\">[Erratum]</a> &nbsp;</nobr>\n        <p></p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n    <table width=\"100%\">\n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td bgcolor=\"#CCE0F9\">\n          <dl>\n            <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/602\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_602\"> Laurent Gillet, Janet S. May, and Philip G. Stevenson</dt>\n            <dd>\n              <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_602\"><i>In vivo</i> importance of heparan sulfate-binding glycoproteins for murid herpesvirus-4 infection</label></strong><br>\n              J Gen Virol 2009 90: 602-613. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/602\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/602\">[Free Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/602\">[PDF]</a> <strong><font color=\"#000090\">IMMEDIATE OPEN ACCESS ARTICLE</font></strong> &nbsp;</nobr>\n              <p></p>\n            </dd>\n          </dl>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody></table>\n    <dl>\n      <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/614\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_614\"> Joanne L. Tan, Norihito Ueda, Andrew A. Mercer, and Stephen B. Fleming</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_614\">Investigation of orf virus structure and morphogenesis using recombinants expressing FLAG-tagged envelope structural proteins: evidence for wrapped virus particles and egress from infected cells</label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 614-625. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/614\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/614\">[Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/614\">[PDF]</a> &nbsp;</nobr>\n        <p></p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n    <dl>\n      <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/626\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_626\"> Eric Schulz, Marc Gottschling, Ignacio G. Bravo, Ullrich Wittstatt, Eggert Stockfleth, and Ingo Nindl</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_626\">Genomic characterization of the first insectivoran papillomavirus reveals an unusually long, second non-coding region and indicates a close relationship to <i>Betapapillomavirus</i></label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 626-633. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/626\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/626\">[Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/626\">[PDF]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/626/DC1\">[Supplementary Material]</a> &nbsp;</nobr>\n        <p></p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n    <dl>\n      <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/634\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_634\"> Parmjeet Randhawa, Raphael Viscidi, Joseph J. Carter, Denise A. Galloway, Tim D. Culp, Cathy Huang, Bala Ramaswami, and Neil D. Christensen</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_634\">Identification of species-specific and cross-reactive epitopes in human polyomavirus capsids using monoclonal antibodies</label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 634-639. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/634\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/634\">[Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/634\">[PDF]</a> &nbsp;</nobr>\n        <p></p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n    <dl>\n      <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/640\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_640\"> Nicolai Bonne, Patrick Shearer, Margaret Sharp, Phillip Clark, and Shane Raidal</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_640\">Assessment of recombinant beak and feather disease virus capsid protein as a vaccine for psittacine beak and feather disease</label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 640-647. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/640\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/640\">[Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/640\">[PDF]</a> &nbsp;</nobr>\n        <p></p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n    <dl>\n      <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/648\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_648\"> Tuija Kekarainen, Laura Martínez-Guinó, and Joaquim Segalés</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_648\">Swine torque teno virus detection in pig commercial vaccines, enzymes for laboratory use and human drugs containing components of porcine origin</label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 648-653. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/648\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90/3/648\">[Full Text]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/reprint/90/3/648\">[PDF]</a> &nbsp;</nobr>\n        <p></p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n    <dl>\n      <dt><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"gca\" value=\"90/3/654\" id=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_654\"> Bart Bryant and Rollie J. Clem</dt>\n      <dd>\n        <strong><label for=\"hw_vir_toc_90_3_654\">Caspase inhibitor P35 is required for the production of robust baculovirus virions in <i>Trichoplusia ni</i> TN-368 cells</label></strong><br>\n        J Gen Virol 2009 90: 654-661. <nobr><a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/abstract/90/3/654\">[Abstract]</a> <a href=\"/vir/cgi/content/full/90